description: A growing crop of Singapore F&B brands is taking a shine to Dubai’s dining scene.  Read more at straitstimes.com.
title: Dubai bling: Singapore restaurants open in the city, while big names from Dubai woo diners here
title_page: Dubai bling: Singapore restaurants open in the city, while big names from Dubai woo diners here | The Straits Times
maintext:
SINGAPORE – As a dining hot spot, desert city Dubai is about to get even hotter.
In the past year or so, the dining scene in the United Arab Emirates (UAE) city has been sizzling – and now some Singapore restaurants are jumping in.
